\cf0 <h3 style="white-space:pre-wrap;">Idaho Reports Podcast \'97 <a href="{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://web.archive.org/web/20260418072956/https://pod.link/IdahoReports"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \ul \ulc4 \strokec4 https://web.archive.org/web/20260418072956/https://pod.link/IdahoReports}}" target="_blank">LISTEN</a></h3><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">Prior to Logan joining the staff, <em>Idaho Reports</em> used an audio hosting site to embed interviews in blog posts and to post an occasional episode of the show. Logan took advantage of the site\'92s existing RSS capability to set up an <em>Idaho Reports</em> podcast which appears on all major podcast platforms. </p><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">After shifting to more consistent distribution and the addition of original podcast episodes, the show\'92s listenership exploded from under 300 plays per year to just over 18,000 plays in 2020 and more than 44,000 plays in 2021. </p>\cell \row

